{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/getsourceremove(tag:)"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/getSourceRemove(tag:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes the source with the given ID from the default main context."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getSourceRemove","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"tag","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You must","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use [method"},{"code":"GLib.Source.destroy","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] for sources added to a non-default main context.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The ID of a [struct"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","isActive":true},{"text":"] is given by [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Source.get_id"},{"type":"text","text":"], or will be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"returned by the functions [method","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.Source.attach","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"], [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.idle_add"},{"type":"text","text":"],"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.idle_add_full","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"], [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.timeout_add"},{"type":"text","text":"],"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[fun